content:
Dinwiddie sent an email to potential investors on Tuesday, a copy of which is obtained by The Block, saying that Tritaurian is “best-suited” to help bring the upcoming securities offering to accredited investors.&nbsp;<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
"Tritaurian is a registered broker-dealer that has worked closely with regulators over the past several years to understand their perspective on blockchain and cryptocurrency," reads the email.&nbsp;
